namespace pdg { /**

\fn pdg::Sprite::makeStatic

\brief make this sprite unaffected by physics (*Chipmunk Physics Only*)

This sprite becomes a static body that isn't affected by physics, though non-static objects can collide with it. This would be used for walls or platforms.

\warning This should be done before setting anything else about the sprite

\returns itself so you can call it on creation


\code
var sprite = layer.createSprite().makeStatic();
\endcode


**/ }